    {
      "id": "troubleshoot-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 595,
      "y": 700,
      "width": 470,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "🔧 Troubleshooting\n• Exit 137 → OOMKilled or node overcommitted\n• Empty logs → crash before output, check node resources\n• Origin not allowed → add URL to allowedOrigins\n• Token missing → add trustedProxies + paste token",
