      "originalText": "🔧 Troubleshooting\n• Exit 137 → OOMKilled or node overcommitted\n• Empty logs → crash before output, check node resources\n• Origin not allowed → add URL to allowedOrigins\n• Token missing → add trustedProxies + paste token",
